<plot>Chittan (Vikram) is born to a vagrant in a cemetary, who dies soon after. Raised with no contact to the outside world except with dead bodies, he grows up inept at social interaction. An acquaintance with a neighborhood drug dealer Gomathi (Sangitha) gets him a job as a handyman in a cannabis farm. Chittan ends up in jail where he makes his first real friendship - with a conman Shakti (Surya). Good performances all-round, especially from Surya as the conman, and from Mahadevan as the cannabis farm owner.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?434142</url></doc>
